column1: '|tstats max(all_statistics.confirmed.value) as count from datamodel=corona_virus by  all_statistics.country  |lookup all_countries_location.csv Country AS all_statistics.country  OUTPUT Country, "IP Address" as dest |search Country="Sierra Leone" OR Country=Liberia OR Country=Guinea |iplocation dest |geostats sum(count) by Country globallimit=0',tstats,admin

'search index=access_index 
| rex field=src_ip (?<CIDR_A>\d+)
| rex field=src_ip \d+\.(?<CIDR_B>\d+)
| rex field=src_ip \d+\.\d+\.(?<CIDR_C>\d+)',rex,admin
